here is my new favorite

00:05:29.310 --> 00:05:32.630
Wallet API, Save card to Google.

00:05:32.630 --> 00:05:36.720
Wallet objects from Google
take physical objects,

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:40.450
like loyalty cards and
offers from your wallet,

00:05:40.450 --> 00:05:42.920
