proliferation.

00:06:20.220 --> 00:06:21.790
Customers are
happier because they

00:06:21.790 --> 00:06:24.530
don't need to carry so many
of their loyalty cards.

00:06:24.530 --> 00:06:27.870
And developers are happier
for connecting these consumers

00:06:27.870 --> 00:06:30.100
to merchants.

00:06:30.100 --> 00:06:33.630
Google Analytics has
introduced Enhanced Ecommerce,

